{"tid":2028532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒指約翰遜將制定計劃不再依賴中國供應醫療物資","createTime":"2020-05-22T00:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T02:30:34.000Z","uid":53003,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2776a7d481e19a2754002339f30e7fb71aec4589","tid":2028532,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:46:58.000Z","msg":"英國《泰晤士報》報道，英國首相約翰遜已指示官員制定計劃，不再依賴中國供應醫療和其他戰略物資。報道指，計劃將由外相藍韜文領導，審視英國在面對潛在敵對外國政府時的經濟和國家安全漏洞，務求讓供應鍵多元化，不再依賴個別國家的非糧食必需品，包括個人防護裝備和藥物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289278&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289278%26csid%3D261_367&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7Bzdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=af411fdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289278&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"6026fc022e1fd259cbe7a6866b4793071f2b503b","tid":2028532,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開始醒"},{"pid":"8b9761509a1f85cbfba4ce70d1f79bb07cb4b3b8","tid":2028532,"uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"The plans, which have been code named &lsquo;Project Defend&rsquo;, include identifying Britain&rsquo;s main economic vulnerabilities to potentially hostile foreign governments as part of a broader new approach to national security<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c959a9ae693dade3f629161752beea8545f71512","tid":2028532,"uid":125724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6026fc022e1fd259cbe7a6866b4793071f2b503b","tid":2028532,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"202